mputer will now search for the file;<br></li><li>If you receive a file named '888poker.exe' under the 'Name' or 'Search Results' section, in the white window, it means the file was found. Double click on it;<br></li><li>If the computer has finished the search and there is no such file in the window, it means that the file was not found. In this case (if you do not have a hard drive other than [C:]), you should repeat the download process.</li></ol><p>For assistance with this, or any of your other online gaming needs, please click here to <a href="https://888-external-en.custhelp.com/app/home/prod/4" target="$$LKContactUsTarget$$">contact us</a>.</p></div></div></div></div> </div></div>   </div>                  </div>                 <div class="column">                     <div class="parsys">                   <div class="sidebar">            <div class="sidebar-component">       </div></div>   </div>                  </div>             </div>                                        </div></div>               </div>      </div> </div></div> <div class="experiencefragment"><div id="experiencefragment-50577197c1" class="cmp-experiencefragment cmp-experiencefragment--internal-footer">  <div class="">     <div class="container-wrapper">                             <div id="container-3f7407d070" class="cmp-container">                  <div class="internal-footer">          <div class="internal-footer-container">                   <div class="internal-footer-title"></div>           <div class="grid-component">         <div class="column-container two-columns-50">                           <div class="column">                 <ul class="internal-footer-ul">                                                                    <li class="internal-footer-list-header">                             <span>                                                                  <a href="/poker-software/">Poker Software</a>                             </span>                         </li> 